    <para><emphasis role="bold">Description:</emphasis> Determines the internet protocol version of the given driver (<parameter>network()</parameter> or <parameter>syslog()</parameter>). The possible values are <userinput>4</userinput> and <userinput>6</userinput>, corresponding to IPv4 and IPv6. The default value is <userinput>4</userinput>.</para>
